descriptionNullable:
**Dataset dictionary**
1. Order ID - ID for each order transaction
2. Customer ID - Name of customer
3. Category - Category of product
4. Sub Category - Sub category of product
5. City - Where the sales transaction occurred
6. Order Date - Date of sales transaction occurred
7. Region - Where the sales transaction occurred
8. Sales (in USD) - sales amount of each sales transaction
9. Profit (in USD) - profit amount of each sales transaction
